in, and Stephen Rivele. (1990). Lieutenant Ramsey's War. Knightsbridge Publishing Co., New York. ASIN: B000IC3PDE\n* Schmidt, Larry. (1982). [http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=ADB068659&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf American Involvement in the Filipino Resistance on Mindanao During the Japanese Occupation, 1942\u20131945]. (PDF). M.S. Thesis. U.S. Army Command and General Staff College. 274 pp.\n* {{cite book|last=Takai|first=K\u014dji|author2=Sakaida, Henry|title=B-29 Hunters of the JAAF|publisher=Osprey Publishing|location=Oxford|year=2001|series=Aviation Elite Units|isbn=1-84176-161-3|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4p1pDSXzZZUC&dq=Raid+on+Yawata}}\n* {{cite book|first=Yuki|last=Tanaka|year=1996|title=Hidden Horrors|publisher=Westview press}}\n* {{cite book|first=Yuki|last=Tanaka|year=1996|title=Poison Gas, the Story Japan Would Like to Forget|work=Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists, October 1988}}\n* {{Cite book | year = 2006 | title = The Knights of Bushido: A Short History of Japanese War Crimes | publisher = Greenhill Books | location = | isbn = 1-85367-651-9}}\n* {{cite book|last=Tillman|first=Barrett|authorlink=Barrett Tillman|title=Whirlwind: The Air War Against Japan 1942\u20131945|publisher=Simon & Schuster|location=New York City|year=2010|isbn=978-1-4165-8440-7|url=https://archive.org/details/whirlwindairwara00till}}\n* {{Cite book | last = Sissons | first = D. C. S. | url = http://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~changmin/documents/Sissons%20Final%20War%20Crimes%20Text%2018-3-06.pdf | title = The Australian War Crimes Trials and Investigations 1942\u201351 | publisher = | location = | isbn = }}\n* {{cite web|title=Wartime Cabinet Document Discloses Conscription of 290,000 Koreans in 1944 |url=http://www1.korea-np.co.jp/pk/033rd_issue/98031103.htm |accessdate=August 20, 2015 |work=The People's Korea |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413200013/http://www1.korea-np.co.jp/pk/033rd_issue/98031103.htm |archivedate=April 13, 2016 }}